item.title: Overview
item.description: Log plugins provide capabilities for querying and visualizing logs against resources, connecting to various log backends to provide a unified view of logs across different systems. warning Omniview is under heavy active development - the LogPlugin SDK is subject to frequent breaking changes until the first stable release.
